### Get a customer by ID
GET http://localhost:8002/customers/2
Accept: application/json

### Check if a customer has enough credit
GET http://localhost:8002/customers/1/credit/500
Accept: application/json

### Deduct credit from a customer
POST http://localhost:8002/customers/1/deduct/500
Accept: application/json

### Restore credit to a customer
POST http://localhost:8002/customers/1/restore/2000000000000000000000000000000000000
Accept: application/json